Package sep.gaia.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BoundingBox
    Interface for a general 2-dimensional rectangle, of which the corners are represented by instances of classes that implement Vector3D.
    Vector3D
    Interface for a general 3-dimensional numerical vector.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgoUtil
    Utility class that provides converting methods between different States (such as GLState, TileState, GeoState).
    FloatBoundingBox
    Class to represent the size of a rectangle by giving the coordinates of the upper left corner and the lower right corner.
    FloatVector3D
    Class to represent a 3-dimensional vector with float coordinates.
    IntegerBoundingBox
    Class to represent the size of a rectangle by giving the coordinates of the upper left corner and the lower right corner.
    IntegerVector3D
    Class to implement a 3-dimensional integer vector for a variety of purposes.
    Logger
    Singleton-class for writing messages into a log-file.
    MeasureConverter
    Class to provide functions that convert internationally diverting measures.
    RayCast
    Utility-class to calculate intersections with the x-y-pane.
